room_title: Escape room "The Great Room" by 13th Hour Haunted House in New York
room_description: This is the Hayden family's room of murders, otherwise known as the Great Room. This massive section of the farmhouse will challenge your wits in all fashions. Multiple sections, secret passageways, and puzzles you never experienced before will have your team running mad. Just be warned: you have only 60 minutes to complete the Great Room and save yourselves. Do you have what it takes?
